720225f-a.text:
Greenwich Street, east side, at Desbrosses Street, showing the express and uptown platforms and the tracks of the 9th Avenue Elevated Line. The photographer is o the downtown platform to
photograph this panoramic view.
June 7, 1940
Views 1,2
P. L. Sperr
